      <title>紧张局势缓和 中国寻求恢复与印度的直航</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-seeks-to-resume-direct-flights-with-india-as-tensions-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部长王毅表示，中国希望恢复与印度的直航，因为经过四年的边界争端僵局之后，这两个亚洲邻国之间的紧张局势正在缓和。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-seeks-to-resume-direct-flights-with-india-as-tensions-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
